d.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218310/extras/b69cce0cae1ed7a2349a18b020dc5f6d.mp4?t=1757972561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >平台跳跃、战斗和解谜巧妙结合，带来让每个玩家都能感受到童年共鸣的复古氛围。探索充满古老谜团和秘密的神秘Ebuzond世界。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手工打造的地牢迷宫</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充满秘密发现的多彩世界</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受世嘉MD启发的16位复古音乐</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >温暖感人的丰富故事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过100种独特宝藏可收集</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
